msgctxt "448_Kiryu"
msgid "Press <Action:Button_Cross@Battingcenter> at the right time to hit the balls pitched by the pitching machine. Hit the home run targets to earn points."
msgstr "Prensa <Action:Button_Cross@Battingcenter> en el momento adecuado para golpear las bolas lanzadas por la máquina de lanzar. Golpea los objetivos de jonrones para ganar puntos."

msgctxt "460_Kiryu"
msgid "There are three targets in the Easy Game. Each target will grant the same number of points, but once a target is hit, it will not be restored until all the remaining targets are also hit."
msgstr "There are three targets in the Easy Game. Each target will grant the same number of points, but once a target is hit, it will not be restored until all the remaining targets are also hit."

msgctxt "472_Kiryu"
msgid "Use <Action:Button_LS_Up@Battingcenter><Action:Button_LS_Down@Battingcenter><Action:Button_LS_Left@Battingcenter><Action:Button_LS_Right@Battingcenter> to aim your swing. If you aim well enough, you can hit two targets at once and earn two times the points."
msgstr "Use <Action:Button_LS_Up@Battingcenter><Action:Button_LS_Down@Battingcenter><Action:Button_LS_Left@Battingcenter><Action:Button_LS_Right@Battingcenter> to aim your swing. If you aim well enough, you can hit two targets at once and earn two times the points."

msgctxt "484_Kiryu"
msgid "Once you hit all the targets, a bonus target will appear. However, you only get one chance to hit it. The bonus target disappears after one pitch, whether you hit it or not. Aim carefully and go for a new high score!"
msgstr "Once you hit all the targets, a bonus target will appear. However, you only get one chance to hit it. The bonus target disappears after one pitch, whether you hit it or not. Aim carefully and go for a new high score!"

